  "detailed_description": "<strong>Claritas</strong> is a 2D, turn-based, party-building dungeon crawler RPG with a variety of unique systems and mechanics.<br><br><strong>Claritas</strong> offers multiple playable characters, each with four unique abilities, allowing for endless strategic combinations.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206870/extras/0e88b570901e8c35ba575ce7a2d5f8dd.poster.avif?t=1746443262\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206870/extras/0e88b570901e8c35ba575ce7a2d5f8dd.webm?t=1746443262\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206870/extras/0e88b570901e8c35ba575ce7a2d5f8dd.mp4?t=1746443262\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your party from a diverse roster of characters, with the flexibility to swap members at any time throughout the game.</p></li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206870/extras/1aa3ce4b33b5ef60ba30a85f7b9b00c8.poster.avif?t=1746443262\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206870/extras/1aa3ce4b33b5ef60ba30a85f7b9b00c8.webm?t=1746443262\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206870/extras/1aa3ce4b33b5ef60ba30a85f7b9b00c8.mp4?t=1746443262\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enhance your heroes' abilities using skill points earned with each level up. You can freely redistribute these points at any time, allowing for flexible customization.</p></li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206870/extras/66ef81d67bdecde76dc4b56fa55bc351.poster.avif?t=1746443262\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206870/extras/66ef81d67bdecde76dc4b56fa55bc351.webm?t=1746443262\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206870/extras/66ef81d67bdecde76dc4b56fa55bc351.mp4?t=1746443262\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on bounty hunting contracts to eliminate specific monsters, earning valuable rewards like experience points, gold, and other bonuses.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206870/extras/cef6a016c57932c08ee95e28180436e4.poster.avif?t=1746443262\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206870/extras/cef6a016c57932c08ee95e28180436e4.webm?t=1746443262\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206870/extras/cef6a016c57932c08ee95e28180436e4.mp4?t=1746443262\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock powerful perks that provide permanent enhancements to your entire party.</p></li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206870/extras/f2922b05961d87b117620882a8e11342.poster.avif?t=1746443262\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206870/extras/f2922b05961d87b117620882a8e11342.webm?t=1746443262\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Encounter unpredictable random events in dungeons, each offering unique choices that lead to different consequences.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Claritas</strong> is a 2D, turn-based, party-building dungeon crawler RPG with a variety of unique systems and mechanics.<br><br><strong>Claritas</strong> offers multiple playable characters, each with four unique abilities, allowing for endless strategic combinations.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206870/extras/0e88b570901e8c35ba575ce7a2d5f8dd.poster.avif?t=1746443262\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206870/extras/0e88b570901e8c35ba575ce7a2d5f8dd.webm?t=1746443262\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206870/extras/0e88b570901e8c35ba575ce7a2d5f8dd.mp4?t=1746443262\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your party from a diverse roster of characters, with the flexibility to swap members at any time throughout the game.</p></li></ul><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206870/extras/1aa3ce4b33b5ef60ba30a85f7b9b00c8.poster.avif?t=1746443262\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206870/extras/1aa3ce4b33b5ef60ba30a85f7b9b00c8.webm?t=1746443262\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3206870/extras/1aa3ce4b33b5ef60ba30a85f7b9b00c8.mp4?t=1746443262\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enhance your heroes' abilities using skill points earned with each level up. You can freely redistribute these points at any time, allowing for flexible customization.</p></li></ul><br><br><spa